com.thomsonreuters.upa.ansipage

Class PageCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.ansipage.PageCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class PageCell
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    PageCell is used to create the building blocks that make up an ANSI Page. These positions, or "cells," are used to construct the layout of each Page object.
